/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce05d9fc648ce3e15e263e645dc236b10b07fb3","tid":2345844,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T05:17:11.000Z","msg":"香港周四（7日）起再度轉冷，至少一連5日都是寒冷天氣🥶🥶🥶🥶🥶<br />\n<br />\n【寒流將再襲港至少5日 天文台料周五濕凍 市區9&deg;C北區4&deg;C】"},{"pid":"622c42bdc91c1105d5315666f9b42983d97e608e","tid":2345844,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T05:46:09.000Z","msg":"幾日凍就打哂飛機，反環保、反全球暖化撚唔肯面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>2020年踏入尾聲，雖然除夕會有強烈寒潮襲港，但環顧整年天氣，香港今年天氣持續暖化，亦再次打破7項天氣紀錄，包括最暖上半年、最熱夏季、最高月平均氣溫、最多全年酷熱天氣日數及最多全年熱夜數目等。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">今年上半年平均氣溫為23&deg;C、平均最高氣溫25.7&deg;C；夏季的平均氣溫高達29.6&deg;C，平均最高氣溫更高達32.6&deg;C；7月更是有紀錄以來最熱的一個月，最高月平均溫度為30.2&deg;C，皆為歷年之冠。其中酷熱天氣警告生效467小時，創20年來最長。天文台預計，今年有機會成為有紀錄以來第二最溫暖的年份。</span><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201228/X74UAHP3FNF3XBGVKDHRNUX6QY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201228%2FX74UAHP3FNF3XBGVKDHRNUX6QY%2F&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=f4317043\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201228%2FX74UAHP3FNF3XBGVKDHRNUX6QY%2F&h=ee6599fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201228/X74UAHP3FNF3XBGVKDHRNUX6QY/</a>"},{"pid":"7ab6bd34b4860e5bc26beeb7caf49ba6fa64c4a7","tid":2345844,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}